vista.set
Class FlagUtils

java.lang.Object
  vista.set.FlagUtils

public class FlagUtils
extends java.lang.Object

A utility class for setting and clearing flags. This involves bit manipulation which is done using bitwise shift, and and or operations.

getLastCheckedBy

public static final java.lang.String getLastCheckedBy(DataSetElement dse)
returns the id of the user if the flag has been marked else return null. The user id is stored in bits 31-25 and is the interpretation of bits 31-25 as 8-1 bit integer in the same order, i.e. bit 31 is the highest order bit and bit 25 is the lowest order bit. Bit 25 is mapped onto bit 1 ( lowest order ) in the interpretation.
